Presented by Doug Batchelor, the "Landmarks of Prophecy" DVD set is a thrilling, 21-part Bible series that gives you keen insight into what lies next in human history, in-depth Bible knowledge, and the practical tools you need to survive and thrive in the here and now! (Includes a bonus set of study guides!)
